Page 2, delete lines 1 through 22, and substitute the following:
"(b)(1) A motion may be filed under this section shall identify and
name as a party the parent for whom services would resume if the child:
(A) Is currently in the custody of the department;
(B) Is not in an adoptive placement, a pre-adoptive
